{"tid":775742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"改革開放40年 林鄭：香港係受惠者  25年前港商億元巨資投向中國如今被“依法”搶光無錢醫治絕症","createTime":"2018-08-11T11:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T10:42:01.000Z","uid":70786,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d42730c08c353d0412268fc348f0b9bd1c35c67","tid":775742,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】今年年底係中國改革開放40周年，愛國傳媒就搞咗個大型圖片展，介紹改革開放有幾重要，而特首林鄭月娥就做主禮嘉賓。林鄭發言時不忘引述國家主席習近平嘅講話，「改革開放只有進行時沒有完成時。沒有改革開放，就沒有中國的今天，也就沒有中國的明天」。<br />\n<br />\n林太由1978年12月講起，話當年中國共產黨第十一屆中央委員會第三次全體會議喺北京召開，定出推行對內改革、對外開放，實現農業、工業、科技和國防現代化，開始咗國家改革開放歷程。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢話香港喺國家改革開放中，不單止係貢獻者，亦係受惠者，話大批港商喺改革開放初期率先投資內地，並作為當時國家嘅對外窗口，以自身優勢為國家輸送資金、人才同管理制度。</span>佢話呢40年嚟，香港一直以自己所長服務國家所需，體現咗與國家「同發展」、「共繁榮」。<br />\n<br />\n25年前港商億元巨資投向中國如今被&ldquo;依法&rdquo;搶光無錢醫治絕症<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/zuGrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/zuGrS</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136e374c93bd78c5db5ff60d022add75648804bf","tid":775742,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"大家記得支持大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定唔會血本無歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57270ffc72b38acb0187dfc682892a208d141420","tid":775742,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:01:42.000Z","msg":"唔知支那吞咗幾多港商家產呢?<br />\n以為偷完技術再過橋抽板係對外國企業先做<br />\n原來對所謂大家都係中國人都係咁做<br />\n唔熟唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家睇清楚淋賤穴娥真面目<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45a55c13d4ea5784cd05518c262db81aef38844","tid":775742,"uid":128603,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/200810_63ebb10e614777bb387c16861c08e887.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F200810_63ebb10e614777bb387c16861c08e887.jpg&h=60f680d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4094227246b36f8125ac642565438d364589e5ed","tid":775742,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"張建宗：香港青年到內地實習後　所有誤解一掃而空<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/buHHFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/buHHFS</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身家就一掃而空"},{"pid":"686d4587ab8580a47be67f5185ce14d84807bf38","tid":775742,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57270ffc72b38acb0187dfc682892a208d141420","tid":775742,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:01:42.000Z","msg":"唔知支那吞咗幾多港商家產呢?<br />\n以為偷完技術再過橋抽板係對外國企業先做<br />\n原來對所謂大家都係中國人都係咁做<br />\n唔熟唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家睇清楚淋賤穴娥真面目<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T10:42:01.000Z","msg":"中國人 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}